Now it needs to become refinement.

There’s an old engineering principle:

The first 90% is invention. The second 90% is simplification.

I think you’re entering the second phase.

If I were maintaining Pantheon, I’d adopt one constitutional rule:

Every addition must either simplify the system, strengthen the system, or prove the system.

Not just expand it.

That’s how frameworks mature.

